faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500e1aabd200ffcbe53ccc84ee701afdf4197b42","tid":2331474,"uid":137768,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"Intel而家咁低價1)主因係佢7nm manufacturing出左問題 delay左 2)Apple/Microsoft會用ARM 架構自己出chip 對Intel乃至x86依賴低左 或者話佢地呢啲Big Tech firms會直接同team RGB競爭 令intel嘅monopoly地位不保 但如果係咁 AMD嘅隱憂更大<br />\n<br />\n1)嘅成因係intel用左太risky嘅方法去整7nm 而如果成功左佢7nm嘅performance會比台積電整到嘅7nm更好 而家話預計2022年推出 但即使係咁5nm 3nm會唔會重蹈覆轍好難講 而家聽講個ceo請求biden去support下呢類local manufacturering 亦都諗緊將部分product交俾台積電整算<br />\n<br />\n2)呢個問題更加嚴重 Intel而家dominate左差唔多成個data center嘅market 亦都係佢地未來重心 因為佢地覺得data center比pc更大return 但如果Google/Apple/Amazon/Microsoft出嘅design比intel更好 Intel嘅client好大機會會離棄Intel 但Intel覺得而家5G edge computing時代個餅會更大 佢唔怕其他公司加入競爭<br />\n<br />\n另外幾點係Intel而家提倡緊XPU嘅concept 亦都啱啱出左第一個GPU同nvidia競爭 加上有mobileye同nio合作緊搞全自動駕駛車 比起tesla佢地更著重safety會用lidar之類嘅tech<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以總結係Intel有太多有focus 而且方向都係有potential huge return 但暫時未知佢地可唔可以come back 下年會好關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c9394609d5a3bce77aac2a1466f5203b5a702d","tid":2331474,"uid":215113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"其實對tsm有冇影響"},{"pid":"6fd52245d0bf621bb6881dea82f13ca50cf111d3","tid":2331474,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"一代晶片王寶座已過！"},{"pid":"b66bf894764d723644b1b06d87343b9125da4890","tid":2331474,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fedcc58c8f9ed848f0d120962aee175d4db66b7","tid":2331474,"uid":34976,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bxuRvi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bxuRvi.gif&h=44b4849d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />